Scope:
Test core features: daily quotes, habit tracker, mood summary, journal, goals, and page navigation.

Objectives:
Ensure app functionality works as expected and UI displays correctly. Detect bugs and document with screenshots.

Areas to Test:
Main Page: Quotes, habit tracker, mood summary.
Inspiring Page: Labels, quotes, images.
Reflection Page: Journal, mood tracker, add habit, goals.
Navigation: Toolbar buttons navigate correctly.

Risks:
Delayed content loading.
UI misalignment or placeholder issues.
Data persistence errors.

Approach:
Manual exploratory testing, plus basic automation via Appium where possible.
